sequenceDiagram
  participant App as Application
  participant OF as OpenFeature SDK
  participant Provider as Local Provider
  participant Audit as Audit Log
  App->>OF: evaluate flag with default and context
  OF->>Provider: provider evaluation call
  Provider->>Provider: resolve file, env override, or bucket
  Provider->>Audit: write redacted JSON Lines event
  Provider-->>OF: value, variant, reason, source
  OF-->>App: typed evaluation result
